## 2. Required Contract

### 2.1 Required ARIA

| Attribute | Value | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `role` | implicit from native element | Don't override |
| `aria-label` | when icon-only | Required for AT |

### 2.2 Required HTML Structure

```html
<button class="...">
  <span class="label">...</span>
</button>
```

### 2.3 Required Token Bindings

The contract token is component-tier; it resolves *through* a semantic token to a primitive. Show all three hops so the cascade is legible:

| Semantic part | State | Component token | → Semantic | → Primitive |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| root | default bg | `<component>.bg.default` | `action.primary` | `{color.blue.6}` → `#2563eb` |
| root | focus ring | `<component>.border.focus` | `focus.ring` | `{color.brand.focus}` → `#ff8040` |

## 3. Interaction States

| State | Visual change | Tokens |
|---|---|---|
| default | base | `action.primary` |
| hover | darken | `action.primary-hover` |
| focus | ring | `focus.ring` outline |
| active | darken further | `action.primary-active` |
| disabled | reduced opacity + aria-disabled | n/a |
| loading | spinner replaces icon, aria-busy | n/a |

