## 5. Do / Don't

**Do:**
- Use the native element (`<button>`, `<input>`)
- Set `aria-label` when icon-only

**Don't:**
- Paint roles on `<div>`s
- Invent new tokens — extend semantic-*.json instead

## 6. Agent Notes

What an AI agent needs to know to safely extend this component:
- Every token in `token_contract` MUST exist in `packages/tokens/src/components/<component>.json` and resolve through a semantic token (component → semantic → primitive)
- Don't bypass Mantine's prop API — extend it
- Storybook or painted-DOM evidence maps to `interaction_states`; any intentional gap must be tracked by `validate:state-coverage`
